  &lt;/Recipe&gt;
&lt;/RecipeData&gt;
</code></pre></p>

CrateEquipmentConditional Spawn a green crate with basic hydroponics setup<pre><code>&lt;Spawn Id="PotatoSupplies"&gt;
  &lt;DynamicThing Id="DynamicCrate"&gt;
    &lt;Color Id="Green"/&gt;
    &lt;Item Id="SeedBag_Potato"&gt;
      &lt;Quantity Value="3"/&gt;
    &lt;/Item&gt;
    &lt;Item Id="ItemHydroponicTray"&gt;
      &lt;Quantity Value="5"/&gt;
    &lt;/Item&gt;
    &lt;Item Id="ItemKitPipeUtilityLiquid"&gt;
      &lt;Quantity Value="1"/&gt;
    &lt;/Item&gt;
    &lt;Item Id="ItemKitPipeLiquid"&gt;
      &lt;Quantity Value="20"/&gt;
    &lt;/Item&gt;
  &lt;/DynamicThing&gt;
&lt;/Spawn&gt;
</code></pre> Spawn emergency equipment in the proper slots<pre><code>&lt;Spawn Id="EmergencyRespawnHuman"&gt;
  &lt;Item Id="ItemEmergencySpaceHelmet" SlotId="Helmet"/&gt;
  &lt;Item Id="ItemEmergencyEvaSuit" SlotId="Suit"&gt;
    &lt;Item Id="ItemGasCanisterEmpty" SlotId="AirTank"&gt;
      &lt;Name Key="SpawnDataOxygenCanister"/&gt;
      &lt;Color Id="White"/&gt;
      &lt;Gas Type="Oxygen" Moles="150" Celsius="20"/&gt;
    &lt;/Item&gt;
    &lt;Item Id="ItemGasFilterCarbonDioxide" SlotId="Filter"/&gt;
    &lt;Item Id="ItemGasCanisterEmpty" SlotId="WasteTank"/&gt;
    &lt;Item Id="ItemBatteryCell" SlotId="LifeSupport"&gt;
      &lt;Charge State="Full"/&gt;
    &lt;/Item&gt;
  &lt;/Item&gt;
  &lt;Spawn Id="EmergencyToolbelt"/&gt;
&lt;/Spawn&gt;
</code></pre> Spawn EmergencyRespawnHuman defined elsewhere when playing as Human on Stationeer difficulty<pre><code>&lt;Spawn Id="EmergencyRespawnHuman" Event="RespawnPlayerKit"&gt;
  &lt;Species Id="Human"/&gt;
  &lt;Difficulty Id="Stationeer" Compare="Equal"/&gt;
&lt;/Spawn&gt;
</code></pre>

Top-Level DefinitionWorld SpawnNested Spawn Define a spawn to be referenced by Id<pre><code>&lt;GameData&gt;
  &lt;Spawn&gt;&lt;/Spawn&gt;
&lt;/GameData&gt;
</code></pre> Define a spawn to execute on a specific Event<pre><code>&lt;GameData&gt;
  &lt;StartCondition&gt;
    &lt;Spawn&gt;&lt;/Spawn&gt;
  &lt;/StartCondition&gt;
  &lt;WorldSettings&gt;
    &lt;World&gt;
      &lt;Spawn&gt;&lt;/Spawn&gt;
    &lt;/World&gt;
  &lt;/WorldSettings&gt;
&lt;/GameData&gt;
</code></pre> <p>Run another spawn (referenced by Id and/or with conditions)<pre><code>&lt;Spawn&gt;
  &lt;Spawn&gt;&lt;/Spawn&gt;
&lt;Spawn&gt;
</code></pre> Run a spawn as a child of an item to fill slots<pre><code>&lt;DynamicThing&gt;
  &lt;Spawn&gt;&lt;/Spawn&gt;
&lt;/DynamicThing&gt;
</code></pre> Run a spawn as a child of a structure to fill slots<pre><code>&lt;Structure&gt;
  &lt;Spawn&gt;&lt;/Spawn&gt;
&lt;/Structure&gt;
</code></pre></p>

Simple ItemCrate Single Potato Seedbag<pre><code>&lt;Item Id="SeedBag_Potato"/&gt;
</code></pre> Green crate with supplies to grow potatoes<pre><code>&lt;DynamicThing Id="DynamicCrate"&gt;
  &lt;Color Id="Green"/&gt;
  &lt;Item Id="SeedBag_Potato"&gt;
    &lt;Quantity Value="3"/&gt;
  &lt;/Item&gt;
  &lt;Item Id="ItemHydroponicTray"&gt;
