  &lt;/Item&gt;
&lt;/DynamicThing&gt;
</code></pre>

Top-Level ItemChild Item Create an item in world, or equipped to the player<pre><code>&lt;Spawn&gt;
  &lt;Item&gt;&lt;/Item&gt;
&lt;/Spawn&gt;
</code></pre> <p>Create an item in a container item<pre><code>&lt;Item&gt;
