&lt;/Structure&gt;
</code></pre></p>

Simple StructureStructure with Children Completed Iron Frame<pre><code>&lt;Structure Id="StructureFrameIron"&gt;
  &lt;SpawnPosition Rule="Explicit"&gt;
    &lt;Offset x="-145" y="39" z="-7" /&gt;
  &lt;/SpawnPosition&gt;
  &lt;BuildState Index="2" /&gt;
&lt;/Structure&gt;
</code></pre> Locker with tools<pre><code>&lt;Structure Id="StructureLockerSmall"&gt;
